cloudy gecko
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a rare gecko found only on Stewart Island and outliers, distinguished by muted patterning in mossy colours.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
